text.tspan: Gabriel used to be insane because he thinks
that time goes fast everyday for him, he was
then captured by one of the spies in

of how he acts, So they put him
in an asylum forever and, he is a bit crazy.
We then gave him a clock-like uniform too,
so he's now our human "clock" that tells
